The script assumes two connected fans, using PWM pins as
noted/configurable within the script.

The script can be set to start on boot by adding it to
`/etc/rc.local`:

```
/usr/bin/python3 <script-loc> &
```

Depends on:

- https://github.com/WiringPi/WiringPi-Python
- wiringpi.com
- https://pypi.org/project/vcgencmd
